title: Banana Boat Sport Cool Zone Sunscreen Continuous Spray SPF 50, 6 Fluid Ounce
description: BANANA BOAT sunscreen ultra mist sport performance cool zone, SPF 50, 6-ounces. Long-lasting continuous spray sunscreen. Cool zone instantly cools and refreshes skin. Broad spectrum UVA or UVB protection. Invisible, rub-free, quick drying, and non-greasy. Very water or sweat resistant.

title: Vidal Sassoon 5-inch Pocket Combs, 2 Count
description: Vidal Sassoon Pocket Comb fits easy in pocket or purse for styling on the go! The fine teeth are best for short hair and sectioning small pieces of hair. Each comb measures 4.875 inches across. Package includes 2 black pocket combs.

title: Vidal Sassoon Family Pack Of 6 Combs
description: Vidal Sassoon Family 6 Pack of combs has a comb for every hair style. Comb styles include large teeth with handle, small teeth with pik handle, 2 large multi-purpose combs with fine and wide teeth, and 2 small combs with fine and wide teeth.
